com.esri.mo2.client.aims
Class FolderItems

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.client.aims.FolderItems
public class FolderItems
extends Object

A utility class that manages a collection of FolderItem objects.
FolderItem objects can be added, removed, changed, and retrieved using this class. This class uses the following classes:

    - BaseEsrimap
    - EsrimapCookieLink
